{"tid":2165832,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[語言偽術]反駁師又要出動","createTime":"2020-08-20T05:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:20:37.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51c5b18d456c4f850e9c810357a03917d31b4329","tid":2165832,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yfiTnp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yfiTnp.png&h=c3c08dc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e37b7657102b4ed1d8f1ee404b00ae137425c28","tid":2165832,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51c5b18d456c4f850e9c810357a03917d31b4329","tid":2165832,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yfiTnp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yfiTnp.png&h=c3c08dc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"有人提出&ldquo;國安法被武器化&rdquo;，她要反駁，正常是拿事實講理據，證明國安法不是被武器化。<br />\n現在，她引來其他範疇，如金融體系及社交媒體都被武器化這現象（假設這描述是真確），來淡化 &ldquo;國安法被武器化&rdquo;。她其實沒有完全否認國安法被武器化，之不過不忍心這觀點太突出，於是找來金融體系與社交媒體作配襯，三者一起被武器化就唔多覺。<br />\n學校是社會的縮影，她的辯駁技倆跟學生相似。<br />\n從前教書，學生甲向我投訴學生乙和學生丙也出貓為何我沒有懲罰他們，學生甲其實承認自己也出貓，只是找兩個同學來陪葬。"},{"pid":"080a762cfd99912155c573c5c6a1363b2be3503d","tid":2165832,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"佢成日偷換概念"}]}